{"tid":1944333,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人妻朱千雪曬素顏自拍照 獲網民盛讚皮膚白滑","createTime":"2020-03-26T10:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T06:59:35.000Z","uid":9573,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"930f007819a1eba63d80b23b8f2c50a2784aaab4","tid":1944333,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"朱千雪去年8月與醫生男友吳昆倫（Justin）在峇里結婚，早前傳出喜訊，不過千雪否認佗B，只表示自己肥胖而已；今早朱千雪在instagram上載自拍照，相中的她以素顏示人，樣子清純﹑精神飽滿，而且皮膚白滑，千雪跟大家講早晨，並表示周日會留在家，早上有幾陣驟雨，局部地區有雷暴。不少圈中人包括蔡思貝﹑岑杏兒﹑唐貝詩和陳凱琳，都留言讚她可愛及皮膚好好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200322/s00009/0840efdfd1da37c126e1b49734b7f922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200322%2Fs00009%2F0840efdfd1da37c126e1b49734b7f922.jpg&h=1826decf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70ab347f75681e3ea5b41cd2bc7dea3305111783","tid":1944333,"uid":198652,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"周日會留在家，早上有幾陣驟雨，局部地區有雷暴。"},{"pid":"12204caf3f7d3fae5d41cdf14f780729043ad47d","tid":1944333,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"菲律賓眼鏡look朱千雪.jpg召喚"},{"pid":"a674cfbdfa8669dd3f1e4c9b370775bfde71bb1b","tid":1944333,"uid":31173,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"睇相成日覺得佢個口應該會好臭"},{"pid":"6e6f43de81a0346b799b28c3f3ef43c14b27e420","tid":1944333,"uid":25758,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"無論化妝同唔化妝都係樣衰<br />\n<br />\n唔明吹奏乜撚"},{"pid":"d481a174073a9e8178880279d786b278f7b1d258","tid":1944333,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:16:07.000Z","msg":"我係A09都睇得出畫左眼線上左粉茶埋唇<br />\n冇化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f570342f299b01c6bc4d293672bf515591ac77","tid":1944333,"uid":56716,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:19: